original_title: Mysterious Doctor Satan The Monster Strikes
overview: Splashed acid burns The Robot's circuitry and sends it out of control. It topples a case of acid on itself and the stunned Copperhead.
tagline: CRAZED WITH THE LUST TO KILL! A power-mad maniac unleashes a lightning attack on an unsuspecting nation...And finds the Copperhead thirsting for revenge!
title: Mysterious Doctor Satan The Monster Strikes
